  "response_text": "The commercial is in high-contrast black and white, focused almost entirely on a young adult woman’s face. She has straight, light-toned hair cut to about shoulder length, with full bangs across her forehead. She wears a dark top and a thin necklace with a small pendant at the base of her neck. At first she faces forward, very near the viewer, with a knowing half-smile and slightly narrowed eyes, as if addressing someone directly in front of her. The background is indistinct and shadowy, with soft, blurred light shapes, giving the scene a private, intimate feeling rather than a clearly identifiable location.\n\nAs she continues, her head turns subtly to one side and back again. Her lips move as she speaks, and her expression shifts between teasing, skeptical, and amused. Dimples appear when she smiles. She holds steady eye contact for much of the time, occasionally lowering her gaze or tilting her chin, then looking back up. The lighting creates glossy highlights in her hair and strong shadows along her cheeks, emphasizing her cheekbones and the line of her bangs.\n\nGradually, a dark vertical shape enters from the right side of the image, as if she is partly seen through a doorway, partition, or shadowed obstruction. It covers the right side of her face and leaves only the left side clearly lit. She remains mostly still behind this dark edge, continuing to speak and react with small changes in her mouth and eyes. At moments she gives a sly smile; at another moment her brow tightens slightly and her expression becomes more serious, almost warning. Near the end, the half-lit look remains: one side of her face is visible, the other fades into darkness. Her expression softens again into a small, controlled smile. No jeans, brand name, or on-screen text are visible in these images; the visual emphasis stays on her face, her dark clothing, the pendant necklace, and the dramatic black-and-white shadows.",
